  </ul>

  <p>
    After making the final adjustments, I exported my Reason song as a WAV file and opened it in Audacity alongside an instrumental version of the original beat.  Through visual comparison between the Zion I track and my remake, you can see I was able to get a pretty close match to the original beat.  Everything sounded good so I'm finished!
  </p>
